        <section class="about" id="about">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="image">
                    <img src="pictures/download (2).jpeg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>why choose us?</h3>
                    <p>The University of Ghana computer science department is the best place to learn about everything concerning computer science.we have well trained lecturers who have at least 5 years experience in the courses they teach.the lecturers are all well trained and they make sure you understand everthing they teach.</p>
                    <p>This is the Information Technology age and at its core is Computer Science. The study of computer science is therefore critical if society is to take full advantage of the benefits Information Technology has to offer and make rapid economic advances. Computer science involves the study and development of applications that allow for our everyday use of computers, the software systems that support these applications, and the means and methods used to produce both applications and systems that behave reliably, correctly and ethically. At the heart of Computer Science lies the skill of computer programming and employers who hire Computer Scientists expect adept programmers with knowledge of current techniques and tools and the ability to apply sound engineering principles to the development, construction and maintenance of computer programs.</p>
                    <p class="mission">our mission</p>
                    <p>Our aim at the University of Ghana's Computer Science Department is to foster a creative and dynamic learning atmosphere that enables students to succeed in the rapidly changing field of computer science. Instilling in our students a solid foundation in theoretical concepts and practical skills, we are committed to cultivating a culture of academic excellence, research, and technological leadership.

                        Three things are the aim of our mission:
                        
                        Academic Excellence: Our dedication lies in offering a thorough and demanding computer science education that gives our pupils the skills, knowledge, and critical thinking abilities they need to tackle challenging problems in the digital age. Our goal is to produce graduates who are eager to pursue a variety of careers in academia, business, and industry by using innovative curriculum design and pedagogical approaches. </p>
                    <a href="#conact" class="btn">contact us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <script src="script.js"></script>
    </body>
